actions.text: Submitted in the Senate, considered, and agreed to without amendment by Voice Vote.

official_title: A resolution relating to printing of the compilation entitled "Majority and Minority Leaders of the Senate" as a Senate document.

summary.text: Authorizes the printing as a Senate document the compilation entitled, "Majority and Minority Leaders of the Senate," including additional copies for the Secretary of the Senate.

titles.title: A resolution relating to printing of the compilation entitled "Majority and Minority Leaders of the Senate" as a Senate document.
